description: The file contains unit tests for the UserSettings component, written using Google Test framework. It tests various UserSettings handler functions, mocking dependencies like Store2Mock, ServiceMock, and others. It verifies both success and failure scenarios for many setter and getter functions related to user preferences and settings.

classes.name: UserSettingsTest
classes.description: Test fixture class for UserSettings related unit tests. Sets up mock dependencies and provides cleanup after tests.
